{"tid":1480252,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"搭鐵慳錢買物資大法 《全民買特惠票》","createTime":"2019-08-17T08:28:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T05:59:45.000Z","uid":270196,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ad2e265d284565f3707c22022e8d70e7d5f9d3f3","tid":1480252,"uid":270196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T08:28:03.000Z","msg":"大家聽日818都會過海（新界九龍人）<br />\n咁車費就會好貴<br />\n小弟建議以下兩種方法<br />\n<strong>818同埋推到每日都做到</strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>1. 練田徑</ins></span></span><br />\n相信呢個對出去發夢嘅人都唔洗介紹<br />\n重點係無人一齊會怯！<br />\n依家引用之前另一個巴打建議<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「每小時00 15 30 45分就一齊用田徑方式入閘」</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>2. 買特惠車票</ins><br />\n（對於唔敢練田徑嘅手足）</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">一來港鐵經常配合警犬話停就停</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">二來港鐵仲未交代車箱清除催淚毒氣方案<br />\n仲要葵芳手足幫佢清潔</span><br />\n我地用返特惠車票都係理所當然<br />\n又可以慳錢比返手足買gear<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知道好多示威者都唔敢去突破呢樣野<br />\n但係人多就會成事<br />\n<strong>諗下你比警犬追緊仲會唔會乖乖地買飛拍卡？</strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>另外有冇法律手足補充以上方法嘅risk</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推到每日都買特惠同練田徑</span></span></em></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40cc905669913ef442f4df7205702a6d78ba4cf1","tid":1480252,"uid":270196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T08:31:44.000Z","msg":"推呀 慳錢買gear <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b319380bc4d198f533bb026063a61cd774cb9fc","tid":1480252,"uid":270196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T09:02:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5105d876c6d7055ea2a39f74ffffc9636a5a75dd","tid":1480252,"uid":270196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:32:18.000Z","msg":"自推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"736538a96cf250beaee90b6f9306ce8714d92089","tid":1480252,"uid":270196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:58:48.000Z","msg":"p牌推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6634d733657a51a7824be258fbd7afb02b742716","tid":1480252,"uid":34899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:14:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0027953f266916a676b3ff86f99c4afe146358b","tid":1480252,"uid":270196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6634d733657a51a7824be258fbd7afb02b742716","tid":1480252,"uid":34899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:14:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:59:45.000Z","msg":"沉到咁都比你搵到呢個po <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}